Author: Goodmorningfatty
Text: Seriously.. if I have to think, I eat some sort of salty carb so my brain can function a little bit, otherwise I’m a dumb fucker when restricting AKA “fasting”.

Author: lover_007
Text: I literally plan eating larger meals around social events so I can be “on” because I’m way too spacey to be socially engaged when I’m heavily restricting. Been doing it this way for 7 years 🙃
